# 2026-05-01 16:22:44.116927
+I am starting fresh with an empty folder. Let's build a white-labeled Universal Privilege Tax system:
+
+Create a .NET solution: dotnet new sln -n UniversalPrivilegeTax.
+
+Create the projects:
+
+dotnet new classlib -n UniversalPrivilegeTax.Core
+
+dotnet new classlib -n UniversalPrivilegeTax.Infrastructure
+
+dotnet new webapi -n UniversalPrivilegeTax.Api
+
+dotnet new xunit -n UniversalPrivilegeTax.Tests
+
+Add projects to the solution and link them (Api -> Infrastructure -> Core).
+
+Initialize a React frontend in src/Frontend using: npm create vite@latest . -- --template react-ts.
+
+Create a TaxSubmission.cs file in UniversalPrivilegeTax.Core/Models/

